<plot>'Gordon Ramsay' (qv) presents a live program in which he intends to prove that a good three-course meal can be cooked within one hour. Accompanied by 'Chris Moyles' (qv), he cooks a three-course meal for a table of guests and encourages viewers to cook along at home, including 'Janet Street-Porter' (qv) and the Big Brother housemates. This is interspersed with a pre-recorded best-out-of-three recipe challenge, in which Gordon competes with 'Alan Carr (I)' (qv), 'Max Beesley' (qv) and 'Mica Paris' (qv).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?220482</url></doc>
